tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
    response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT,
    respondent_name VARCHAR(50),
    response_date TIMESTAMP,
    response_data JSON
);

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
    response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT,
    respondent_id INT,
    response_text TEXT,
    response_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE survey_response (
  response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  respondent_id INT,
  question_id INT,
  response_text TEXT,
  response_date TIMESTAMP
);
